      "Text": "Security update for libzypp",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for libzypp fixes the following issue\n\n- CVE-2026-25707: Handcrafted repo metadata may cause arbitrary local files to be overwritten (bsc#1259802).\n- CVE-2026-44942: Fixed possible path traversal attacks via .repo files 'path=' entries (bsc#1267874). \n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
